## What {{.Name}} is

Three surfaces, one binary:

- **CLI** — interactive + scriptable. Stable schemas, structured errors,
  preview via `--dry-run`, queries parse via `--explain`.
- **Capability surface** — `{{.Name}} spec --format json` emits a
  machine-readable manifest of every command, its inputs, outputs, side
  effects, and idempotency. Agents drive {{.Name}} from this, not from
  `--help`.
- **Library** — `import "{{.Module}}"` and use the same primitives from
  your own Go code.

Conformance proof: [`docs/12-factor-conformance.md`](docs/12-factor-conformance.md)
(auto-regenerated by `make conformance`).

